    "Lemma 2 (Factor Price Frontier (FPF)).",
    "For a given automation index I, the factor price frontier slopes downwards, starting from a limiting point w * (I) =",
    "Increases in A move the FPF proportionately outwards.",
    "Increases in I raise w * (I) and swivel the factor price frontier clock-wise.",
    "We obtain the factor price frontier from the aggregate cost function, which is the dual of the aggregate production function."
